[{"Id": 1021065, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": "It has been narrated that whenever Hazrat Ali (a) may face any problem and difficulty in his important work then He (a) use to recite 2 rakat namaz (like fajr) and then recite 100 times ASTAGH-FERUL-LAAH and after that He use to recite this dua and then start the work by which He never use to face any problem and difficulty…", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Manqool hai keh jab Hazrat Ali (a) ko koi nehaayat pareshaan aur be-chain karne waala kaam dar pesh aata to Aap (a) 2 rakat namaz (fajr ki tarah) adaa kar ke 100 martaba ASTAGH-FERUL-LAAH padhne ke baad is dua ko padhte thay us ke baad apne kaam ko shuru farmate thay. Jis ki wajah se Aap ko kisi kaam mein nuqsaan aur pareshaani nahin hoti thi…", "UrduDescription": "منقول ہے کہ جب حضرت علیؑ کو کوئی نہایت پریشان کن اور اضطراب آگئیں مہم درپیش ہوتی تھی تو آپ ۲ رکعت نماز ادا کر کے ۱۰۰ مرتبہ استغفراللہ پڑھنے کے بعد دعائے ذیل کو پڑھتے تھے اس کے بعد اپنے کام (تدبیر) کو شروع فرماتے تھے۔ جسکی وجہ سے آپ کو کسی کام میں نقصان اور پریشانی نہیں ہوتی تھی۔۔۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicR